---
---

<!-- WHO WE ARE — full-width cinematic opener -->
<section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-end pb-20 pt-40 overflow-hidden bg-black">
  <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.4) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.8) 70%, #000 100%);"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6 md:px-16">
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-amber mb-6">WHO WHE ARE</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl lg:text-[7rem] font-black tracking-tighter leading-none mb-10">
          SOUTHLIGHT<br/>PICTURES
        </h1>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-amber/40 pl-6">
          <p>
            SouthLight Pictures is an American production company founded by Alex Caruso at the beginning of 2026. SouthLight Pictures aims to create compelling stories that push the boundaries of entertainment.
          </p>
          <p>
            We craft experiences that resonate with audiences around the globe. Alex Caruso believes in the power of narrative to inspire. With a commitment to quality and innovation, we constantly evolve and challenge the conventions of storytelling.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
        <img
          src="/soutlight-pictures-website/logo.png"
          alt="SouthLight Pictures"
          class="w-full max-w-4xl opacity-90 select-none ml-16"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- THE FOUNDER — editorial split layout -->
<section class="bg-black pt-4 pb-32">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-16">

    <!-- Label -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-16">
      <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-gray-500">The Founder</span>
      <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-white/10"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main grid: text left, photo right -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-0 items-start">

      <!-- Text column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 lg:pr-16">
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-2 leading-none">Alex</h2>
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-10 leading-none text-amber">Caruso</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
          Alex Caruso's interest in film began as a child after he discovered the power of telling stories. When he moved to the United States as a teenager, he began directing horror short films, such as <em>Alone</em>, <em>The Shadow</em>, and <em>The Whistler</em>. Since then, he has written a horror TV show and feature movies.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-xl mt-5">
          Selected to be one of the best first-time filmmakers in London and the best narrative short in Hollywood, Alex is now developing thriller and horror movies. His interest in the Catholic culture made him write and explore faith-based storytelling. Alex has built SouthLight Pictures into a production company dedicated to crafting unforgettable cinematic experiences that captivate audiences worldwide.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Photo column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 mt-12 lg:mt-0 lg:-mt-32 relative">
        <div class="aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden rounded-3xl">
          <img
            src="https://cdn.boldjourney.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/c-PersonalAlexCaruso__mefoto2_1706138798091.jpg"
            alt="Alex Caruso"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top grayscale-[20%]"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- Decorative amber line -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 left-0 w-16 h-1 bg-amber"></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
